name: Ver.0.7.33
body:
- Added dark theme
- Added setting to screen orientation
- Added setting to change playback UI
- Changed the behavior of back button of toolbar

name: Ver.0.7.32
body:
- IPv6 support.
- Use orientation information of EXIF when displaying photos.

name: Ver.0.7.31
body:
- Support for Android 8.1
- Fix some crash factors

name: Ver.0.7.30
body: - Fixed an issue where Play / Pause on PinP did not work

name: Ver.0.7.27
body:
- Add content deletion function (It depends on the spec and settings of the media server)
  You can use it by enabling [Settings] → [Function] → [Delete content]. (Default off)
- Support for use over wired LAN connection
- Support for control by DPAD
- Change behavior when decode error
- Fixed some bugs
